Savedsearch.name: username
Savedsearch.queryStr: log.msrcid = 'OCI Audit' and log.udfs46 != oracle_casb_service_account | stats count by log.udfs46

Savedsearch.name: Put_Post_Delete_Event_Tail_10
Savedsearch.queryStr: log.msrcid = 'OCI Audit' and log.udfs16 in (post, delete, put, head) | stats count by log.udfs11 | tail 10

Savedsearch.name: OriginIP_Top10
Savedsearch.queryStr: log.msrcid = 'OCI Audit' | timestats count as logrecords by log.udfs32 | sort -logrecords | head 10

Savedsearch.name: User Access Detail
Savedsearch.queryStr: log.msrcid = 'OCI Audit' and log.udfs46 != oracle_casb_service_account and log.udfs46 != null | stats count by log.udfs46, log.udfs32, log.udfs12, log.udfs35 | sort -Count
